Standards-Version: 3.9.3

Package: gitfs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, fuse3, libgit2-1.9, python3-dev, python3-distutils, gcc
Description: Mount git repositories as local folders
 gitfs is a FUSE file system that fully integrates with git. You can mount a
 remote repository's branch locally, and any subsequent changes made to the
 files will be automatically committed and pushed to the remote.
